WEBVTT

00:49.841 --> 00:52.260
EPISODE 8

00:54.846 --> 00:56.222
Don't do this.

00:57.015 --> 00:58.141
Gyu-min,

00:58.516 --> 01:00.769
please don't do this.

01:03.146 --> 01:05.857
What are you trying to do?

01:06.441 --> 01:07.901
What do you want?

01:08.985 --> 01:10.278
I'm going to die.

01:11.821 --> 01:13.948
I'm going to die with you.

01:17.243 --> 01:19.412
Come on, move. Move.

01:20.288 --> 01:21.706
Get out of the way.

01:34.719 --> 01:35.720
MS. TAMBOURINE'S BOYFRIEND

01:40.975 --> 01:41.893
Hello?

01:42.977 --> 01:45.104
- Yes, I know who you are.
- If we start it on this day,

01:45.480 --> 01:47.106
- we should be able to get it done.
- Yes.

01:54.239 --> 01:55.782
- Dong-u.
- Yes?

01:56.699 --> 01:58.076
What do you think is going on?

02:01.079 --> 02:02.163
I think she's in love.

02:03.957 --> 02:04.874
Right?

02:08.169 --> 02:09.963
Then is it really true?

02:11.714 --> 02:13.800
My gosh, is she really seeing someone?

02:15.301 --> 02:16.636
Does that even make sense to you?

02:21.391 --> 02:22.976
You didn't talk to her at all today?

02:23.184 --> 02:24.185
No.

02:24.602 --> 02:26.729
Did something happen to Jin-a?

02:27.647 --> 02:29.107
I can't get a hold of her.

02:31.192 --> 02:32.986
I thought something happened.

02:33.444 --> 02:35.613
It's not like she's a kid.
I'm sure she's fine.

02:36.489 --> 02:38.825
I know how much you care about her,
but don't spoil her.

02:38.950 --> 02:40.034
All right.

02:40.743 --> 02:43.913
If she comes to the office or calls you--

02:43.997 --> 02:45.331
I'll let you know right away.

02:45.957 --> 02:47.167
Thank you.

02:48.459 --> 02:50.003
Don't worry too much.

02:51.087 --> 02:52.046
All right.

04:12.001 --> 04:13.419
Oh, hello.

04:13.503 --> 04:15.338
I need to go into Seung-ho's room
for a moment.

04:15.421 --> 04:17.465
- I see.
- Thank you.

04:17.674 --> 04:18.549
Come in.

04:22.929 --> 04:25.098
- There.
- Oh, that's okay.

04:29.686 --> 04:32.105
My gosh, Jun-hui. Welcome.

04:32.188 --> 04:34.190
What brings you here?
Are you here to eat with us?

04:34.274 --> 04:37.151
No, I have to install something
on Seung-ho's computer.

04:37.402 --> 04:40.863
I see. He plays computer games
all the time when he should be studying.

04:40.989 --> 04:42.573
And you're encouraging him.

04:42.740 --> 04:44.534
Just this once. Can I go into his room?

04:44.659 --> 04:45.868
Yes, go ahead.

04:52.083 --> 04:53.251
What's the matter?

04:53.459 --> 04:54.669
It's nothing.

05:11.394 --> 05:12.812
What's Lee Gyu-min's phone number?

05:14.647 --> 05:15.732
Just give me his number.

05:16.816 --> 05:18.401
Why do you need his number?

05:18.484 --> 05:19.694
Just give it to me.

05:21.654 --> 05:23.031
Gosh, I don't know his number.

05:23.656 --> 05:25.491
But why do you ask?
Did something else happen?

05:26.034 --> 05:27.160
I... I don't know either.

05:27.243 --> 05:29.454
Just hurry up and find his number...
Damn it.

05:30.204 --> 05:33.207
I do have his business card,
but it's at home.

05:34.083 --> 05:35.126
Where did you put it?

05:35.376 --> 05:39.088
Well... I think I put it
in one of the drawers under my desk.

05:40.548 --> 05:42.592
Hey, what the heck is going on?

05:44.927 --> 05:46.721
- I found it.
- What?

05:46.804 --> 05:47.972
You found it?

05:48.681 --> 05:50.558
You're in my room now?
Are you at my place?

05:51.517 --> 05:53.478
- Seung-ho, I have to go.
- Hey, wait--

05:57.857 --> 05:59.901
Gosh, what the hell is he up to?

06:23.800 --> 06:26.552
Can we pull over for a minute?

06:27.512 --> 06:29.138
I feel so nauseous right now.

06:30.932 --> 06:34.268
I'm serious. I feel like throwing up.

06:34.352 --> 06:35.311
Pull over, please.

06:35.394 --> 06:36.979
Do you think I'm an idiot or what?

06:43.945 --> 06:45.446
Jun-hui, have some fruit with us.

06:45.530 --> 06:47.865
I'm sorry, Ms. Kim.
Something came up, so I have to go.

06:47.949 --> 06:49.325
- Have a good evening.
- Hey, wait.

06:49.408 --> 06:51.202
- Just let him leave.
- But still...

06:51.285 --> 06:52.370
Hey, Jun-hui.

06:59.502 --> 07:02.213
I feel like you know
something I don't know.

07:02.630 --> 07:04.132
What are you talking about?

07:05.383 --> 07:07.260
He said something came up.

07:28.823 --> 07:30.700
Pull over or answer your phone!

07:32.368 --> 07:35.079
Hey. Stop ignoring me, will you?

07:36.080 --> 07:38.958
- Who the hell keeps calling?
- Pull over!

07:39.041 --> 07:40.209
We could get into an accident.

07:41.294 --> 07:43.004
- Pull over right now.
- Who the hell is this?

07:47.884 --> 07:48.885
Hello?

07:48.968 --> 07:50.470
You're with Jin-a now, aren't you?

07:52.680 --> 07:55.308
Who the hell is this?
Who the fuck are you?

08:44.398 --> 08:47.109
Are you all right? Are you okay, Jin-a?

08:47.985 --> 08:49.070
Let me see.

08:50.071 --> 08:51.739
You're bleeding.

08:57.787 --> 09:00.289
We have to get back on the road.
We won't die from this.

09:00.373 --> 09:02.416
Hey, you're bleeding right now.

09:02.959 --> 09:06.379
Drive even faster so that we can roll off
a cliff together or something.

09:06.587 --> 09:09.298
Why are you being like this?
Have you lost your mind?

09:09.382 --> 09:11.217
You said you wanted to die with me.
Let's do it!

09:11.884 --> 09:13.928
I'll grant your wish and die with you.

09:14.262 --> 09:16.639
Come on. We don't even have to go far.

09:16.764 --> 09:19.058
- I'll die with you right here.
- Hey, enough.

09:19.141 --> 09:20.601
You crazy bitch!

09:24.605 --> 09:25.731
How dare you swear at me!

09:26.899 --> 09:29.110
You have no right to talk to me like that.

09:52.466 --> 09:53.509
Hello?

09:54.719 --> 09:56.971
Jin-a. It's you, right?

09:58.139 --> 09:59.056
Yes,

09:59.807 --> 10:00.850
it's me.

10:02.101 --> 10:03.269
Where are you?

10:03.811 --> 10:04.979
Where are you now?

10:06.355 --> 10:08.608
Something happened, right?
Something must have happened.

10:10.192 --> 10:11.068
Yes.

10:13.154 --> 10:14.447
Where are you?

10:15.656 --> 10:17.617
Jin-a, where are you right now?

10:25.291 --> 10:26.500
Thank you.

10:26.959 --> 10:28.377
You should go to a hospital first.

10:30.212 --> 10:31.380
Please get in.

11:00.910 --> 11:02.578
It hurts.

11:12.254 --> 11:15.257
I'm looking for Yoon Jin-a.
She was taken in after a car accident.

11:16.384 --> 11:17.551
She's being examined.

11:17.635 --> 11:19.553
Go through that door
and it's on your right.

11:27.603 --> 11:29.230
- I'm going to kill you.
- Hey.

11:29.397 --> 11:31.607
- I swear I will end you!
- Break it up.

11:34.902 --> 11:36.195
Calm down.

11:36.362 --> 11:39.073
I have to question him for the accident.
You can talk to him later.

11:39.740 --> 11:40.825
Come.

11:45.204 --> 11:46.205
Later.

11:50.084 --> 11:51.877
That little...

11:59.927 --> 12:02.054
CT ROOM

12:02.138 --> 12:04.640
Doctor. Is Yoon Jin-a...

12:05.266 --> 12:06.642
- She's getting changed.
- Okay.

13:00.446 --> 13:01.739
You're okay, right?

13:02.865 --> 13:03.949
Yes.

13:06.368 --> 13:07.661
Okay, then.

13:10.206 --> 13:11.373
I'm sorry.

13:16.879 --> 13:18.130
Let's get changed.

14:09.682 --> 14:12.017
Are you doing all the work yourself?

14:12.851 --> 14:15.396
Ask your boss to give you a raise.

14:15.854 --> 14:18.816
Okay, then. Take care.

14:19.692 --> 14:21.569
- Was that Jin-a?
- Yes.

14:21.902 --> 14:24.572
She might spend the night at the office.

14:24.822 --> 14:26.866
She has some reports to write up.

14:27.575 --> 14:32.538
Gosh, I wonder if she'll ever find
the time to get married.

14:33.497 --> 14:34.665
Goodness.

14:36.041 --> 14:37.585
Oh, my.

14:44.633 --> 14:47.511
Has Gyeong-seon not heard
from his father yet?

14:48.345 --> 14:50.848
I guess not since she never mentioned him.

14:52.016 --> 14:55.436
It's only going to give her
a headache if he calls now.

14:56.353 --> 14:58.689
The kid he had with his third wife

14:58.772 --> 15:01.025
probably just started elementary school.

15:03.360 --> 15:05.279
He had a child with his second wife too.

15:05.654 --> 15:07.197
Exactly.

15:07.907 --> 15:10.159
Whom he gets married to
is none of my business.

15:10.326 --> 15:12.828
They could've grown old together,
just the two of them.

15:12.912 --> 15:16.206
But why do they have to have children
when he has full-grown ones already?

15:16.749 --> 15:18.375
Gyeong-seon's mother was in torment

15:18.459 --> 15:20.794
even on her deathbed
because of his infidelity.

15:21.587 --> 15:24.214
Gyeong-seon got so sick and tired of that.

15:24.298 --> 15:27.051
That's why she won't date or get married.

15:29.094 --> 15:30.763
But Jun-hui should get married.

15:31.805 --> 15:33.599
He should.

15:34.516 --> 15:37.227
But what kind of woman would marry him?

15:37.478 --> 15:39.521
His family tree is a mess.

15:40.105 --> 15:42.524
Honestly, imagine if it were us.

15:42.650 --> 15:44.485
Will you let Jin-a marry into that family?

15:44.693 --> 15:46.445
I'd rather have her end up a spinster.

15:46.654 --> 15:48.489
It's nonsense.

15:59.583 --> 16:01.251
It's still bleeding,
so apply pressure on it

16:01.335 --> 16:03.128
- and remove it later.
- Okay.

16:04.171 --> 16:07.299
Ma'am, here. Thank you
for letting me borrow your phone.

16:19.937 --> 16:22.982
- Tell me if you need anything.
- Thank you.

16:31.615 --> 16:35.911
What did you do
with the patient on bed number four?

16:37.913 --> 16:39.289
They said I can go now.

16:40.874 --> 16:43.168
- Are you going to be okay?
- Yes.

19:03.142 --> 19:04.184
What is it?

19:05.602 --> 19:06.770
Are you angry?

19:08.313 --> 19:09.231
No.

19:11.733 --> 19:12.943
Yes, you are.

19:14.111 --> 19:15.404
Not right now.

19:17.698 --> 19:19.449
Then why won't you say anything?

19:28.000 --> 19:29.376
Can you look at me?

19:31.128 --> 19:32.337
What is there to look at?

19:37.009 --> 19:38.886
You weren't like this at the hospital.

19:42.514 --> 19:44.016
I was too overwhelmed to get angry.

19:47.936 --> 19:51.148
So now that you are not,
you are getting angry?

19:53.108 --> 19:54.234
I'm not angry.

19:55.944 --> 19:58.447
Then why won't you even look at me?

19:59.865 --> 20:01.783
I said I'm sorry.

20:03.243 --> 20:04.244
Okay.

20:09.791 --> 20:11.501
Just yell at me or something.

20:12.628 --> 20:14.087
That would be better.

21:04.596 --> 21:05.806
What is it?

21:12.980 --> 21:13.855
Jun-hui.

21:16.483 --> 21:19.361
I was sure that something
must have happened to you.

21:21.488 --> 21:23.448
I hoped that I'd be wrong.

21:26.702 --> 21:28.370
I felt like I was going crazy.

21:30.831 --> 21:32.207
I regretted it so much.

21:34.418 --> 21:36.378
I should've just bought you a new phone.

21:38.714 --> 21:40.257
I should've gone to pick you up.

21:42.342 --> 21:43.719
I shouldn't have left you alone.

21:51.351 --> 21:52.978
You got me worried.

22:06.158 --> 22:08.493
I realized
that I really can't live without you now.

22:37.773 --> 22:40.400
I was going to get all mad
and yell at you,

22:41.777 --> 22:43.278
but I missed the right timing.

22:45.697 --> 22:48.658
Anger is bad for your health.

22:52.120 --> 22:53.705
If you know that,

22:54.081 --> 22:55.916
why do you get yourself in trouble
all the time?

22:56.500 --> 22:58.668
Well, that's

22:58.835 --> 23:01.338
what keeps our relationship

23:01.421 --> 23:03.757
so exciting, don't you think?

23:07.052 --> 23:08.261
I hate you.

23:09.387 --> 23:11.223
What? You hate me?

23:12.974 --> 23:14.101
You'll regret saying that.

23:14.976 --> 23:16.103
I don't think so.

23:16.686 --> 23:17.646
Are you sure?

23:18.313 --> 23:21.608
I called my parents and told them
that I can't come home tonight.

23:23.193 --> 23:26.196
Right, you hate me,

23:26.279 --> 23:30.242
so you probably don't even care
whether I go home or not.

23:37.040 --> 23:37.916
Let's hurry.

24:43.440 --> 24:46.026
My gosh, you sure love to drink alone.

24:46.985 --> 24:48.445
Aren't these beers from my place?

24:48.653 --> 24:51.031
Yes, I brought them all.

24:52.490 --> 24:53.825
Did you just get home from work?

24:54.159 --> 24:55.160
Yes.

24:56.912 --> 24:59.080
It doesn't look like
you came straight from work.

25:00.040 --> 25:02.334
I'm old enough to know
that I shouldn't fall for that trick.

25:02.959 --> 25:04.002
Oh, boy.

25:05.795 --> 25:09.007
Hey, did you see Jin-a today
by any chance?

25:09.382 --> 25:11.092
No. Why do you ask?

25:12.427 --> 25:15.138
I can't get a hold of her

25:15.222 --> 25:17.807
because her phone is broken. I miss her.

25:19.267 --> 25:20.352
She's like your boyfriend.

25:21.269 --> 25:24.731
No, I love her more
than I would love my own boyfriend.

25:26.316 --> 25:28.360
Why don't you date someone?

25:30.237 --> 25:31.655
Forget it.

25:33.657 --> 25:35.200
Are you going to stay single forever?

25:35.575 --> 25:39.204
Why? Are you worried
that I'd depend on you when I'm old?

25:40.121 --> 25:41.957
Don't you worry.

25:42.374 --> 25:45.043
I won't be a burden to you.

25:45.126 --> 25:46.544
That's not what I meant.

25:47.295 --> 25:49.381
You should meet a nice guy

25:49.464 --> 25:51.466
and fall in love, don't you think?

25:51.549 --> 25:53.635
I don't believe in love.

25:54.386 --> 25:56.846
That's the only thing I learned from Dad.

26:04.688 --> 26:07.816
We cut all ties with him,
so he's out of our lives for good now,

26:09.025 --> 26:12.237
but you'd better not live like him
because I'll teach you a serious lesson.

26:20.120 --> 26:21.663
Finish that and leave.

26:22.831 --> 26:23.957
I'm going to bed.

27:00.618 --> 27:01.703
What are you doing here?

27:01.828 --> 27:03.747
I was worried
Gyeong-seon might come with you.

27:06.416 --> 27:08.793
How did you even take a shower
if you were that anxious?

27:09.002 --> 27:11.504
I washed up quickly
because I sweated so much earlier.

27:12.213 --> 27:13.673
Do you have smaller pants?

27:20.221 --> 27:21.389
That's it?

27:31.024 --> 27:32.817
I didn't want to worry you,

27:32.901 --> 27:35.028
so I tried to sort it out
on my own as soon as possible,

27:35.111 --> 27:36.321
but it got out of hand.

27:36.654 --> 27:38.448
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

27:41.242 --> 27:45.163
I'm not saying we should share everything
just because we're in a relationship.

27:45.955 --> 27:47.248
I don't even want that.

27:47.791 --> 27:51.044
There's a line we shouldn't cross.
However,

27:53.171 --> 27:57.008
what happened this time wasn't something
you needed to hide from me.

27:59.469 --> 28:00.929
I know that I made a mistake.

28:02.764 --> 28:05.809
I guess I thought
that I knew everything about him.

28:10.855 --> 28:12.399
Because you guys shared everything?

28:16.945 --> 28:19.697
Well, isn't that what everyone does

28:19.989 --> 28:22.033
when they're in a relationship?

28:22.784 --> 28:24.661
For example,

28:24.744 --> 28:27.831
some couples have joint accounts

28:27.914 --> 28:30.333
or open savings accounts together.

28:35.296 --> 28:39.759
You've never done things like that
with your ex-girlfriends?

28:41.177 --> 28:42.971
I don't think I ever did anything

28:43.304 --> 28:45.056
just because everyone else does it.

28:49.602 --> 28:52.021
Then will you say no if I suggest
we should do something

28:52.147 --> 28:54.065
that all couples do?

28:55.191 --> 28:56.693
Why are you being so unreasonable?

28:56.776 --> 28:58.611
I'm not being unreasonable.

28:59.112 --> 29:02.157
Well, fine.
I'll never suggest anything, then.

29:03.950 --> 29:05.493
Why do you have to twist it like that?

29:06.995 --> 29:08.621
I'm not making anything up here.

29:08.705 --> 29:10.623
You said that's what you want.

29:11.166 --> 29:13.168
Then I should respect that.

29:13.251 --> 29:15.128
I can't make you do
what you don't want to do.

29:18.965 --> 29:20.133
Let's change the topic.

29:20.216 --> 29:23.344
No, tell me more. What's different
about the relationships you've been in?

29:23.511 --> 29:25.680
Tell me what was so special about them.

29:25.847 --> 29:27.098
Let's...

29:29.100 --> 29:30.560
Let's just go to bed.

29:31.436 --> 29:33.229
Go ahead. I want to drink more.

30:31.830 --> 30:34.332
Gosh, I think
I'm getting a headache again.

31:43.109 --> 31:44.402
I was just...

31:45.945 --> 31:49.574
embarrassed and ashamed of what happened,

31:50.199 --> 31:52.201
so I ended up taking it out on you.

31:56.539 --> 31:59.334
I'm already regretting

32:00.043 --> 32:02.086
how stupid I was in the past.

32:03.588 --> 32:08.217
But it sounded like
you were adding on to that,

32:08.509 --> 32:10.678
so it made me get angry.

32:15.683 --> 32:19.687
I'm already upset for upsetting you,

32:21.856 --> 32:25.652
and I'm sorry for making you worry.

32:27.028 --> 32:28.363
That's why...

32:32.825 --> 32:34.035
Are you really sleeping?

32:54.514 --> 32:55.723
Say it to me out loud.

32:58.518 --> 32:59.686
Say it.

33:00.019 --> 33:01.562
- You're so petty.
- Come on.

33:01.980 --> 33:03.523
Forget it. I'm not going to say it.

33:15.535 --> 33:16.619
Jun-hui.

33:18.997 --> 33:20.581
Jun-hui, it's me.

33:21.582 --> 33:22.875
Turn that off.

33:23.126 --> 33:25.294
- Hey.
- I just wanted to record you something

33:26.129 --> 33:29.007
- since I have your phone with me.
- No, I don't want to listen to this.

33:30.049 --> 33:32.385
- Please don't do this to me. Turn it off.
- Thank you.

33:32.719 --> 33:33.761
No.

33:34.387 --> 33:36.723
- Stop it.
- Thank you for caring about me

33:37.348 --> 33:38.558
and loving me.

33:39.183 --> 33:41.227
- Gosh, I don't want to listen to this.
- That's why

33:41.394 --> 33:43.021
- when someone's in love,
- I can't.

33:44.272 --> 33:45.940
- Turn it off.
- they should love like you do.

33:47.191 --> 33:48.901
- I can't take this.
- Jun-hui.

33:52.655 --> 33:53.781
I love you

33:56.200 --> 33:57.535
with all my heart.

33:58.494 --> 33:59.620
I'll love you longer.

34:00.747 --> 34:01.873
I will love you...

34:02.040 --> 34:04.417
And I'll love you more.

34:05.001 --> 34:06.210
...for a long time.

35:33.422 --> 35:37.176
EMPLOYEE SATISFACTION
AND WORKPLACE DISCRIMINATION SURVEY

35:38.636 --> 35:40.012
Where are the survey results?

35:41.180 --> 35:44.100
Employees working outside the office
haven't handed them in yet.

35:45.893 --> 35:48.271
- Where are we going to have the dinner?
- I don't think

35:49.021 --> 35:50.982
they've decided on that either.

35:53.693 --> 35:56.529
Pleasing women is the hardest thing to do.

36:07.582 --> 36:08.666
Come in.

36:25.308 --> 36:26.851
You need to face the consequences

36:27.727 --> 36:29.061
for eavesdropping.

36:30.438 --> 36:31.647
What do you...

36:32.481 --> 36:34.317
How would I ever dare to...

36:34.400 --> 36:37.195
I'm sorry if I made you think that way.

36:37.737 --> 36:38.863
I'm really sorry, sir.

36:43.409 --> 36:44.410
Do you think that will do?

36:44.869 --> 36:46.078
Well, I do have more.

36:46.954 --> 36:49.081
I think you should give
the female employees bonuses

36:49.540 --> 36:53.794
instead of holding the dinner.

36:55.963 --> 36:57.131
And why should I?

36:57.506 --> 36:59.133
I think the majority of them

36:59.425 --> 37:01.219
are refusing to attend company dinners.

37:05.014 --> 37:06.682
That means they've really had enough.

37:12.480 --> 37:13.314
How much is it?

37:13.397 --> 37:15.524
I wrote that I no longer want
to attend company dinners.

37:16.484 --> 37:17.818
I think everyone did.

37:18.653 --> 37:20.571
I wrote that I'll follow the majority.

37:21.530 --> 37:23.074
I just left it blank.

37:24.825 --> 37:27.870
Even the four of us wrote different stuff,
so how can we ever reach a consensus?

37:29.538 --> 37:30.748
And why did you leave it blank?

37:31.707 --> 37:34.252
I wrote down everything that happened
including the names.

37:34.585 --> 37:35.628
Excuse me.

37:36.170 --> 37:37.713
Excuse me.

37:38.130 --> 37:39.257
- Welcome.
- Hello.

37:40.299 --> 37:41.592
Here you are.

37:42.218 --> 37:43.177
Hello.

37:45.096 --> 37:46.931
- Enjoy your meal.
- Thank you.

37:48.266 --> 37:50.393
It feels empty without Ms. Yoon.

37:52.770 --> 37:54.188
- Ma'am.
- Yes?

37:54.272 --> 37:56.315
- Three fermented soybean soup, please.
- Okay.

37:56.983 --> 37:59.777
By the way, who's she dating?

38:02.113 --> 38:04.282
Is she dating someone?

38:04.699 --> 38:07.326
Yes, she's completely head over heels.

38:07.868 --> 38:09.787
She told me everything.

38:13.249 --> 38:14.375
What?

38:15.334 --> 38:16.794
Do you know anything?

38:17.378 --> 38:18.879
No, I'm in shock myself.

38:31.976 --> 38:33.102
You don't want to go?

38:34.478 --> 38:35.563
No.

38:37.064 --> 38:39.942
Don't you know that China
has the biggest market?

38:40.818 --> 38:43.738
Gaming and animation markets
are rapidly growing in China.

38:43.821 --> 38:45.573
It's our chance
to expand into new markets.

38:46.574 --> 38:49.410
I know that,
but why does it have to be me?

38:50.328 --> 38:52.163
We need to make a proposal.

38:52.455 --> 38:53.664
We got an offer from China.

38:54.081 --> 38:56.208
They offered to collaborate with us.

38:56.292 --> 38:57.626
It's a great opportunity.

38:59.628 --> 39:00.796
You should send someone else.

39:02.173 --> 39:04.133
It wouldn't be as long
as your last stay in the US.

39:04.216 --> 39:06.052
You just need to be there
for a few months.

39:06.302 --> 39:08.304
I really can't go.

39:08.846 --> 39:09.930
You can't?

39:10.264 --> 39:11.974
Why can't you go?

39:13.434 --> 39:14.769
I want to stay with my girlfriend.

39:17.813 --> 39:18.773
Have you gone mad?

39:20.816 --> 39:24.070
Okay, fine.
I'll admit that dating is important.

39:24.820 --> 39:29.283
But come on. It's not even for a year.
It's just for three months.

39:30.701 --> 39:33.245
- I still can't go.
- Do you want me to just fire you?

39:35.206 --> 39:36.874
- Fine, go ahead.
- What?

39:38.918 --> 39:41.045
- I have work to do. I'll excuse myself.
- Hey.

39:42.380 --> 39:43.631
I have something to do.

39:53.349 --> 39:55.643
Hey, did you piss off the CEO?

39:55.810 --> 39:57.269
The team manager's going to kill you.

40:00.564 --> 40:03.442
Plus, what's so bad about
going on a business trip?

40:04.527 --> 40:07.154
You're right.
That's why you should go instead.

40:07.446 --> 40:11.242
Hey, don't cause any trouble.
Just do what they tell you to do.

40:12.201 --> 40:13.244
Jun-hui.

40:13.994 --> 40:16.455
Why are you making a big deal
out of having a girlfriend?

40:18.707 --> 40:21.001
Is that why you refused to go?
Because of Geum--

40:22.128 --> 40:23.212
Who?

40:23.671 --> 40:27.007
I mean, he's not going to be gone forever.
Aren't I right?

40:28.175 --> 40:31.011
You can't convince me to go.
You'll need to send someone else.

40:31.762 --> 40:33.556
You might get fired for real.

40:35.015 --> 40:36.392
Do you want my resignation letter?

40:39.687 --> 40:42.898
- Hey, what are you doing?
- I should write one.

40:48.612 --> 40:50.489
Don't be so hard on yourself.

40:50.990 --> 40:52.783
Everyone regrets their past.

40:53.826 --> 40:55.536
I'm not regretting.

40:56.287 --> 40:59.498
I just can't believe
that I once went out with that guy.

41:00.583 --> 41:03.127
I'm just disappointed in myself.

41:04.170 --> 41:06.505
But you wised up and chose Jun-hui.

41:08.007 --> 41:09.467
That's not true.

41:09.550 --> 41:12.344
I just fell for him without knowing it.

41:13.179 --> 41:17.016
And thankfully,
he hasn't made me regret it yet.

41:18.392 --> 41:20.644
I can't guarantee the future,

41:21.395 --> 41:23.147
but I think you two will last a long time.

41:23.230 --> 41:24.231
Really?

41:24.648 --> 41:26.817
Jun-hui loves you so much.

41:26.901 --> 41:28.235
It's amazing.

41:28.652 --> 41:30.154
I knew you were going to tease me.

41:30.821 --> 41:32.531
I'm not teasing. I'm amazed.

41:32.907 --> 41:35.618
I told you that he called me
when he couldn't reach you.

41:36.076 --> 41:38.120
Looking back, something didn't
feel right back then.

41:39.455 --> 41:40.623
Like how?

41:40.706 --> 41:42.333
I answered half-heartedly.

41:42.416 --> 41:45.211
I said it's not a big deal for an adult
to miss a few phone calls.

41:45.544 --> 41:47.880
And I thought he was overreacting.

41:48.380 --> 41:51.926
But I think he sensed
that something was not right.

41:58.974 --> 42:00.726
You must be very happy.

42:03.854 --> 42:07.107
I really am. It's almost intimidating.

42:20.955 --> 42:24.750
- Thank you.
- Number 257, please come to the window.

42:26.794 --> 42:27.795
Have a nice day.

42:27.878 --> 42:30.548
We understand, but...

42:30.965 --> 42:32.299
Welcome.

42:37.555 --> 42:39.640
- Number 258.
- Have a nice day.

42:41.058 --> 42:43.477
Customer number 258?

42:46.063 --> 42:48.607
Please fill in the marked items.

42:48.691 --> 42:49.984
Can I have your photo ID, please?

42:50.776 --> 42:53.279
- Thank you.
- Customer 259, please come to the counter.

42:56.865 --> 42:58.158
Have a nice day.

43:02.329 --> 43:05.416
Customer 273, please come to the window.

43:25.603 --> 43:26.687
Goodbye.

44:37.591 --> 44:39.009
Hello.

45:10.332 --> 45:11.250
Jin-a.

45:22.803 --> 45:24.555
- You're doing it again.
- How did you know?

45:25.556 --> 45:26.932
I'm not falling for that again.

45:31.145 --> 45:32.688
I should take my shoes off.

45:35.524 --> 45:36.775
You can't get me.

45:44.408 --> 45:45.451
You little...

45:55.335 --> 45:57.171
Should we have gone together to buy this?

46:00.090 --> 46:01.925
The sooner you get it, the better.

46:02.551 --> 46:03.635
Good job.

46:04.219 --> 46:07.181
You went through a lot of trouble today.

46:08.599 --> 46:11.310
You won't have to worry from now on.

46:11.393 --> 46:12.811
Everything has been sorted out.

46:14.938 --> 46:16.732
Then I should try my best for us.

46:17.900 --> 46:19.401
You are already doing it.

46:21.069 --> 46:24.781
Bo-ra told me
that you were really worried about me.

46:24.865 --> 46:26.867
You always get into trouble
when you're alone.

46:27.659 --> 46:29.411
I told you I pulled myself together.

46:33.665 --> 46:36.210
When do you get off from work
after you go back to the office?

46:38.253 --> 46:41.924
There's a meeting among female employees,
so I can't miss it.

46:44.468 --> 46:47.387
That's bad news. But what meeting?

46:51.642 --> 46:53.227
Are you in some kind of a secret society?

46:54.853 --> 46:55.854
No.

46:57.564 --> 46:59.983
Regarding sexual harassment
in the office...

47:00.609 --> 47:03.529
Everyone is hesitant
about reporting sexual harassment cases.

47:03.946 --> 47:07.074
I understand them.
I used to be like them too.

47:08.617 --> 47:10.202
That means you no longer are.

47:10.744 --> 47:14.623
Yes. I'm trying hard to change.

47:17.125 --> 47:20.546
I'm trying because I don't want you
to worry about me.

47:21.421 --> 47:22.631
That's touching.

47:23.048 --> 47:24.383
This is nothing.

47:24.633 --> 47:26.760
Yes. It's not quite enough.

47:27.302 --> 47:28.345
What?

47:30.180 --> 47:33.141
I don't want to hide our relationship
anymore.

47:35.143 --> 47:37.271
Let's make it public before we get caught.

47:44.444 --> 47:45.696
Don't worry. I'll do it.

47:47.406 --> 47:48.865
Why leave me out of it?

47:53.870 --> 47:54.997
Oh, you.

47:59.793 --> 48:01.878
That's not the only thing.

48:02.379 --> 48:03.672
You know about this too.

48:03.755 --> 48:05.716
He came out of nowhere
and started touching my arm.

48:06.341 --> 48:08.427
- I feel like throwing up.
- Me too.

48:08.510 --> 48:10.554
I told him to stop, but he won't.

48:10.637 --> 48:12.764
- That's enough.
- But there's more.

48:12.848 --> 48:15.142
Ms. Choi in the Purchasing Team
was going to the restroom...

48:16.852 --> 48:20.022
- Oh, no. Was that when...
- All right. Stop.

48:21.898 --> 48:24.151
When I told you to write it up,
you didn't do anything.

48:25.152 --> 48:26.820
Should I just record everything?

48:27.613 --> 48:28.447
That's a good idea.

48:29.740 --> 48:31.074
It could be more impactful.

48:31.742 --> 48:35.245
We're the victims. Why are we hiding?
We don't need to be ashamed of anything.

48:39.207 --> 48:40.542
Did Ms. Tambourine just say that?

48:42.210 --> 48:43.045
I did.

48:45.339 --> 48:46.423
You heard it right.

48:50.886 --> 48:52.054
PORK RINDS

48:52.137 --> 48:54.389
It's not just our company.

48:54.473 --> 48:56.391
Other companies are having the same issue.

48:57.059 --> 48:59.394
You know, Mr. Na of that dairy company...

48:59.478 --> 49:01.938
He got sued for sexual harassment
in the workplace.

49:02.606 --> 49:03.774
Women are scary.

49:04.358 --> 49:05.651
We should be careful too.

49:06.151 --> 49:08.570
- Why are the portions so small?
- One more soju, please.

49:09.154 --> 49:10.822
- Actually,
- Coming!

49:10.906 --> 49:13.283
I won Yoon Jin-a over to our side.

49:15.077 --> 49:16.078
You did?

49:16.787 --> 49:18.580
How did you do it?

49:18.664 --> 49:21.375
I talked her into it.

49:21.458 --> 49:23.460
I said I was only trying
to get along with everyone.

49:23.543 --> 49:25.712
I told her she must understand.

49:27.172 --> 49:28.423
Then what?

49:28.757 --> 49:30.425
Did she buy it?

49:31.218 --> 49:32.344
Of course she did.

49:34.346 --> 49:35.347
I also told her

49:37.224 --> 49:40.727
that she should cut you some slack
as well.

49:41.103 --> 49:44.022
I asked her for all of us then and there.

49:47.192 --> 49:49.027
Dong-u, there's no meat on the grill.

49:49.111 --> 49:49.945
Oh, right.

49:50.946 --> 49:51.947
I'm sorry, sir.

49:53.365 --> 49:56.618
Jin-a was so good at this.

49:56.993 --> 49:59.579
She knew how to please Mr. Nam.

50:06.878 --> 50:08.755
- Goodbye.
- Thank you.

50:09.673 --> 50:10.716
Thank you, Mr. Nam.

50:10.799 --> 50:12.509
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

50:13.176 --> 50:14.511
Thank you.

50:14.803 --> 50:17.389
Shall we go do karaoke for a second round?

50:18.432 --> 50:20.058
Let's go home early.

50:23.812 --> 50:26.356
Mr. Nam, I'll come with you. Mr. Nam!

50:26.857 --> 50:29.067
How about we go by ourselves?

50:30.986 --> 50:32.654
We're all guys here. It's no fun.

50:34.823 --> 50:37.284
Let's just go. Let's go.

51:04.519 --> 51:08.690
Through the cigarette smoke
And the glamorous outfit

51:08.815 --> 51:12.319
What I see in the mirror is

51:12.736 --> 51:16.573
I see myself worn out
In this life so different

51:16.823 --> 51:20.827
And you, you are forgotten

51:22.037 --> 51:24.122
Turn me back to the old me

51:24.206 --> 51:28.752
Back to who I was before I met you

51:29.377 --> 51:32.672
You hurt me so deeply

51:32.756 --> 51:36.134
That I just can't let go of it

51:36.218 --> 51:37.928
I hope

51:38.011 --> 51:42.974
That you meet someone who's just like you

51:43.058 --> 51:48.313
If you ever fall in love again

51:52.609 --> 51:57.781
Am I invisible because of her?

51:59.699 --> 52:04.079
This love is so painful

52:06.873 --> 52:11.837
That I can't breathe

52:14.881 --> 52:21.388
I'll wish you happiness

52:21.888 --> 52:28.186
I'll pray with all my soul

52:30.146 --> 52:33.942
If you leave me because you loathe me

52:34.025 --> 52:37.696
I will let you go without a word

52:38.113 --> 52:41.867
I'll pick an armful of azaleas

52:41.950 --> 52:45.453
And strew them over your path

52:46.079 --> 52:49.875
When you leave me

52:49.958 --> 52:53.712
Please tread softly on them

52:53.795 --> 52:58.008
If you leave me because you loathe me

52:58.091 --> 53:02.554
I'll never shed a single drop of tear

53:23.158 --> 53:24.659
- Hello.
- Hello.

53:25.327 --> 53:27.746
I'm here to meet my boyfriend.

53:28.288 --> 53:30.498
Oh, I see. Have a good night.

53:30.832 --> 53:31.958
Good night.

53:57.108 --> 53:57.984
My gosh.

54:02.447 --> 54:03.782
Gosh, look at my face.

54:05.283 --> 54:06.576
I look horrible now.

54:08.954 --> 54:10.330
Why is this in my purse?

54:21.508 --> 54:22.759
Isn't that a tambourine?

54:23.593 --> 54:25.011
- Is that...
- Why is this here?

54:43.488 --> 54:44.614
You're so hot.

54:46.032 --> 54:48.284
What? What did you say?

54:48.827 --> 54:49.869
Nothing.

54:51.705 --> 54:53.665
- You must be bored.
- Don't come here.

54:54.165 --> 54:55.959
You look perfect now. Stay right there.

54:56.876 --> 54:57.961
Keep working.

54:59.546 --> 55:00.922
I'll be done soon. Just a moment.

57:27.068 --> 57:28.486
I'm here, dude.

57:45.170 --> 57:47.005
- Hey, did you...
- Oh, no.

57:47.088 --> 57:48.173
Hey, what...

57:50.842 --> 57:51.885
Hey.

58:01.269 --> 58:04.063
What should I do now? What was I thinking?

58:11.613 --> 58:13.156
Gosh.

58:14.115 --> 58:15.158
Hey.

58:15.492 --> 58:19.120
Don't overreact when she comes back, okay?

58:20.038 --> 58:22.624
- Okay?
- Don't overreact? Look who's talking.

58:23.791 --> 58:27.462
My gosh, how could the two of you...
I feel so betrayed.

58:32.383 --> 58:33.343
What?

58:41.100 --> 58:42.894
Hello... I mean,

58:43.478 --> 58:45.522
I'm sorry about that, Ms. Yoon.

58:45.897 --> 58:47.690
- Don't worry about it.
- Thank you.

58:54.822 --> 58:57.492
So I guess I should...

59:00.161 --> 59:05.500
- Congratulations
- Hey, stop it.

59:06.042 --> 59:09.170
- Congratulations
- I told you to stop.

59:09.295 --> 59:11.798
- May your relationship
- Hey, seriously.

59:11.881 --> 59:14.676
- Last forever
- I'm sorry.

59:17.470 --> 59:19.847
- It looks like he's very drunk.
- Yes, he is so drunk.

59:19.931 --> 59:21.140
Hey, you should...

59:22.016 --> 59:23.560
- Where did you get this?
- What?

59:23.643 --> 59:24.811
- This.
- The tambourine?

59:36.239 --> 59:37.490
I will...

59:38.992 --> 59:40.159
tell my parents.

59:43.788 --> 59:45.039
Let's tell them together.

59:47.292 --> 59:50.378
No, I can do it alone. I'll be fine.

59:54.048 --> 59:56.050
Then I'll tell Gyeong-seon--

59:56.467 --> 59:58.011
I want to tell her myself.

59:58.595 --> 59:59.679
I should.

01:00:01.139 --> 01:00:04.726
She'll feel so betrayed
when she finds out.

01:00:04.851 --> 01:00:06.561
If I keep hiding behind you,

01:00:07.312 --> 01:00:08.813
she'll be even more disappointed in me.

01:00:10.773 --> 01:00:11.774
To tell you the truth,

01:00:12.942 --> 01:00:16.654
I'm more worried about how she will react
than how my parents will.

01:00:17.322 --> 01:00:18.990
She means so much to me.

01:00:20.950 --> 01:00:22.869
She might be okay with it
because she knows that.

01:00:24.829 --> 01:00:28.416
I really hope so.
That will make me very happy.

01:01:10.041 --> 01:01:11.334
Can we talk for a few minutes?

01:01:24.972 --> 01:01:27.809
- I heard you met up with Jun-hui.
- What are you going to do now?

01:01:28.643 --> 01:01:32.397
I didn't know
that things would come this far.

01:01:33.898 --> 01:01:36.693
Fine, it somehow ended up like this.

01:01:37.235 --> 01:01:38.403
But...

01:01:39.445 --> 01:01:40.822
What are you going to do now?

01:01:41.447 --> 01:01:44.075
It's only a matter of time
before Mom and Dad find out.

01:01:44.826 --> 01:01:46.619
I heard even Gyeong-seon doesn't know yet.

01:01:47.203 --> 01:01:48.788
Jun-hui told me that he doesn't care.

01:01:49.122 --> 01:01:51.165
He's just saying that.

01:01:51.249 --> 01:01:52.709
My gosh.

01:01:53.084 --> 01:01:56.045
Why do you always cause trouble
every time you date someone?

01:01:56.129 --> 01:01:57.672
What did I do?

01:02:01.175 --> 01:02:02.093
Anyway,

01:02:03.177 --> 01:02:05.763
I'm thinking about telling Mom and Dad.
What do you think?

01:02:05.847 --> 01:02:07.974
Consider yourself lucky
if they don't kick you out.

01:02:10.852 --> 01:02:12.395
To be honest, I'm not sure about Dad.

01:02:13.104 --> 01:02:14.605
But I'm sure about how Mom will react.

01:02:15.273 --> 01:02:16.816
She'll at least pass out.

01:02:20.236 --> 01:02:21.404
I mean...

01:02:22.196 --> 01:02:24.615
No one knows what will happen
between you guys.

01:02:27.618 --> 01:02:30.621
But what if you guys break up?

01:02:33.583 --> 01:02:36.836
Don't you know that we'll have to cut ties
with Jun-hui and Gyeong-seon forever?

01:02:38.254 --> 01:02:40.006
I won't let that happen.

01:02:41.132 --> 01:02:42.759
That's just your wish.

01:02:43.050 --> 01:02:44.552
Do you think you guys are special?

01:02:44.719 --> 01:02:46.220
You aren't any different from others.

01:02:47.555 --> 01:02:48.681
We're different.

01:02:49.432 --> 01:02:50.808
It's going to be different,

01:02:51.350 --> 01:02:54.145
so what you're worrying about
will never happen.

01:03:11.537 --> 01:03:12.538
I mean...

01:03:13.748 --> 01:03:17.084
Seriously. Why did he have to say
that we might break up?

01:03:17.502 --> 01:03:19.670
It's as if he can't wait
to see us breaking up.

01:03:25.009 --> 01:03:26.886
Are we forbidden to date each other?

01:03:26.969 --> 01:03:28.888
Why? What's wrong with that?

01:03:29.222 --> 01:03:31.724
Right. There's nothing wrong
with us dating.

01:03:32.058 --> 01:03:35.102
Yes. You're right.

01:03:35.895 --> 01:03:36.979
I'm right.

01:03:38.940 --> 01:03:40.900
What a joke.

01:03:40.983 --> 01:03:43.027
Jin-a, have confidence.

01:03:47.698 --> 01:03:51.285
Do you even talk to yourself
while brushing your teeth now?

01:03:51.994 --> 01:03:56.791
My gosh, who in the world
is going to marry you?

01:03:58.835 --> 01:04:00.837
Seo Jun-hui.

01:04:02.296 --> 01:04:04.298
- What?
- What? What's wrong?

01:04:05.216 --> 01:04:07.218
- What did you just say?
- Nothing.

01:04:08.302 --> 01:04:11.180
Be quiet on your way to your room.
Seung-ho's studying.

01:04:11.639 --> 01:04:12.515
Goodness.

01:04:15.059 --> 01:04:16.310
My gosh.

01:04:26.028 --> 01:04:27.154
Mom. Dad.

01:04:28.865 --> 01:04:30.449
I'm dating Jun-hui.

01:04:33.995 --> 01:04:35.913
Mom, I'm seeing Jun-hui.

01:04:36.622 --> 01:04:39.292
And you guys can't stop me.
I'm still going to date him.

01:04:39.375 --> 01:04:40.751
I am...

01:04:41.961 --> 01:04:44.380
seeing someone right now.

01:04:45.047 --> 01:04:46.340
And that is...

01:04:47.842 --> 01:04:49.176
Jun...

01:04:51.345 --> 01:04:53.014
I'm dating Jun-hui.

01:04:54.056 --> 01:04:55.182
We're dating.

01:04:55.474 --> 01:04:57.643
You won't be able to stop us.

01:04:57.727 --> 01:04:58.853
We're going to keep dating.

01:04:59.937 --> 01:05:02.857
Go kill yourself!

01:05:02.940 --> 01:05:04.609
I'm really sorry.

01:05:05.359 --> 01:05:07.069
I'm dating Jun-hui.

01:05:07.153 --> 01:05:08.946
I didn't know this would happen.

01:05:09.488 --> 01:05:11.574
I know it's my own heart.

01:05:11.657 --> 01:05:13.618
But I couldn't control it.

01:05:14.493 --> 01:05:15.912
I couldn't stop myself.

01:05:15.995 --> 01:05:18.706
I'm also going through a hard time.

01:05:19.999 --> 01:05:21.792
Can't you just understand me?

01:05:21.876 --> 01:05:23.085
Are you sure you'll be fine?

01:05:24.503 --> 01:05:25.630
Tell me if you need help.

01:05:26.005 --> 01:05:27.965
I'll go to your house
instead of going to work.

01:05:28.466 --> 01:05:30.509
You really don't need to.

01:05:30.593 --> 01:05:32.345
I can do it on my own.

01:05:34.138 --> 01:05:37.808
I know you can. I just don't feel good
about you doing it alone.

01:05:38.309 --> 01:05:41.020
They won't beat me up, right?
I'm all grown up now.

01:05:43.272 --> 01:05:45.316
Am I supposed to stay still
even if you get beaten up?

01:05:46.400 --> 01:05:48.152
You can come and watch.

01:05:52.323 --> 01:05:53.908
How are you so confident?

01:05:54.116 --> 01:05:56.077
It's like you have faith in something.

01:05:56.744 --> 01:05:59.205
Yes, I do have faith in myself.

01:06:03.918 --> 01:06:05.962
I thought you would say
you have faith in me.

01:06:07.254 --> 01:06:09.507
Of course, I have faith in you.

01:06:09.799 --> 01:06:12.218
You're the only one
who will forever be on my side.

01:06:12.468 --> 01:06:14.428
You're such a sweet-talker.

01:06:15.179 --> 01:06:16.973
I'm sweet in every way.

01:06:17.348 --> 01:06:18.432
I'm going to hang up.

01:06:19.016 --> 01:06:20.351
You say that too often.

01:06:21.602 --> 01:06:22.770
You're sweet.

01:06:24.563 --> 01:06:27.733
Let me ask you one last time.
Can you really do it alone?

01:06:28.317 --> 01:06:30.236
My gosh, that's enough. Bye.

01:08:12.129 --> 01:08:13.214
Come in.

01:08:22.223 --> 01:08:23.224
What are you doing?

01:08:23.724 --> 01:08:25.559
What? Oh, well...

01:08:26.602 --> 01:08:29.980
I'm separating my old notebooks
from my recent ones.

01:08:35.194 --> 01:08:36.237
Where's Mom?

01:08:37.696 --> 01:08:39.031
At an herbal clinic with Seung-ho.

01:09:02.596 --> 01:09:04.014
Don't you have something to tell me?

01:09:14.733 --> 01:09:16.068
I told you

01:09:17.528 --> 01:09:21.282
that I'm ready to listen
to whatever you have to say.

01:09:23.617 --> 01:09:25.578
You can tell me anything.

01:09:36.297 --> 01:09:37.548
Dad.

01:10:08.329 --> 01:10:09.747
Where's Jun-hui?

01:10:14.210 --> 01:10:15.211
What?

01:10:40.861 --> 01:10:42.071
You're not crying, are you?

01:10:42.655 --> 01:10:44.281
Please don't scold Jun-hui.

01:10:44.365 --> 01:10:46.075
Do you like him that much?

01:10:46.700 --> 01:10:50.412
Please check him too.
He's like a son to me.

01:10:50.704 --> 01:10:52.122
- My mom will definitely faint.
- Gosh.

01:10:52.206 --> 01:10:53.415
You'll witness that soon.

01:10:53.499 --> 01:10:55.918
I'll let it slide if you bring me
any evidence regarding that.

01:10:56.001 --> 01:10:59.255
I've always been nothing but nice to you,
Ms. Yoon.

01:10:59.338 --> 01:11:01.966
- Do you have time tonight?
- Don't mind me.

01:11:02.091 --> 01:11:03.509
Who is it?

01:11:03.592 --> 01:11:05.427
- Seo Jun-hui.
- What?

01:11:05.511 --> 01:11:06.428
Her boyfriend.

01:11:06.512 --> 01:11:07.763
- Why?
- What?

01:11:07.846 --> 01:11:09.223
What?

01:11:09.890 --> 01:11:10.849
Gyeong-seon.

01:11:10.933 --> 01:11:12.977
I can't live without you.

01:11:13.269 --> 01:11:15.312
Don't give Jin-a a hard time.

01:11:15.854 --> 01:11:17.564
I only thought about Jun-hui.

01:11:18.941 --> 01:11:20.859
I did not take anyone else
into consideration.

01:11:22.236 --> 01:11:24.196
That's how we ended up like this.

01:11:27.533 --> 01:11:29.535
Subtitle translation by Lee Ja-won
